b'As a single mom, sometimes it\xe2\x80\x99s hard to make ends meet. Our Internet for Good program helps connect families in need with high speed internet. For moms like Katelyn, it helps take some of the financial stress away so she can focus on her son. #TELUSGivesBack'

b'Half of Canadian single mothers live in poverty. Our Internet for Good program connects families in need with high speed internet for less than $10/month to help them succeed and focus on what matters most - their family. #TELUSGivesBack'

b'This year, we\xe2\x80\x99ve given $150 million to support Canadians through COVID-19, offering access to virtual mental health programs, providing families with food and protective supplies, and connecting isolated seniors with loved ones. #TELUSGivesBack'

b"Our team is buzzing with excitement. We're investing $100M in the boldest and bravest innovators tackling Canada's biggest social challenges with the launch of the TELUS Pollinator Fund For Good. b'We\xe2\x80\x99ve been recognized by @wsj as the 15th company in the world in the category of social capitalism leadership. b'Leaving foster care isn\xe2\x80\x99t always easy. b'Now that Gold River, BC, is connected, we can proudly say that every town in the province with a population over 1,000 has access to our world-leading network. b"We're expanding the TELUS Mobility for Good:trade_mark: program nationally. In partnership with @cafdn, we're giving free phones and plans to youth who have aged out of foster care so they can stay connected to what matters most."

b'We are firm in our stance against racism and violence and are adding our voices in solidarity to speak out against racial injustice in the United States, Canada, and around the world. b'Our Chief Neuroscience Officer Dr. Diane McIntosh has a few tips for how to protect your mental health during #Covid19. #MentalHealthWeek :purple_heart:
.
:alarm_clock:  Maintain a routine - regular bedtimes, work schedules and healthy meals.
.
:flexed_biceps:  Get your heart pumping with exercise, whether it\xe2\x80\x99s a fitness video or dancing to a favourite song.
.
:sun_with_face:  Go outside if you can do so safely. No outdoor space? Open a window and let the fresh air in!
.
:partying_face:  Schedule fun in your day - refresh your spirits with a good book or video call with a friend.
.
:brain:  Be mindful by being kind to yourself, taking frequent breaks and checking in on how you\xe2\x80\x99re feeling.
.
:laptop_computer:  If in doubt, check it out. Remember to only seek information from trusted sources.
.
For more ways to protect your mental health during #Covid19, head to telus.com/stayconnected. :purple_heart:'
